  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "1 - Lobby Up, Landlubbers: Are you shore you want to rot in the lobby?
    \nPick Captains or Crew and hit \"Ready\" so the Host can get this ship sailin'!\n\n2
    - Host, use your last two brain cells to hit the + and - buttons and set the
    trophy goal. Don\u2019t pick a number too high, we know you can\u2019t count
    past ten anyway!\n\n3 - The Cards Don't Have Legs: If you\u2019re staring at
    an empty table, \ndon\u2019t just sit there like a dead fish. Cards can't deal
    themselves! \nBark at your lazy Host to smash that card box. \nBe rude about
    it, they\u2019re clearly slacking!\n\n4 - Signal Your Mate: Collect 4 of a kind
    and signal your companion\nuse an emote, scream in the mic, or do a stupid dance.
    \nIf your partner isn\u2019t a complete bilge rat, \nthey\u2019ll smash the LOOT
    button and you\u2019ll get paid.\n\n5 - Brains Over Boots: If the other crew
    members are smarter than you\nand catch you first, you\u2019re getting booted
    right on your salty butts!\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
