      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "10 - No Crybabies: Whining is strictly prohibited on this ship.\nIf you\u2019re
    gonna cry, go back to your mommy.\n\n11 - Stay in Your Seat: Do not abandon ship!
    Remain seated until the bitter end or\nprepare to walk the plank.\n\n12 - Move
    it or lose it: Play as fast as your greasy fingers can move. \nThis is a pirate
    raid, not a retirement home chess match ! \nIf you want to think for ten minutes,
    go play with your grandma!\n\n13- Enjoy the voyage, you filthy bilge rats ! \nDon\u2019t
    forget to flaunt your sorry sails on Skullstagram, tag us @shiftplaygamesofficial
    \nso we can mock your pathetic loot !! \nor just stay quiet and drown!"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
