  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "5 - The \"Vibe Check\" Re-deal: If the whole crew agrees that \"something
    is wrong\" and hits Pass,\nthe Host needs to hit the cards again. (See rule #5:
    Cards. Don't. Have. Legs.)\nSit Down or Shut Up: All cards must be seated before
    you even think about calling a 'Pass.'\n\n6 - Communication for dummies (Keys
    1-5): Don\u2019t just sit there like a wooden leg!\n Smash keys 1 - 5 to throw
    some signs at your mate.\n\n7 - Don't lose your noggin (Literally)\nIf your head
    decides to pop off and take a little vacation, stay calm! \nIt\u2019s just a
    flesh wound. Your ugly mug will bounce back to your neck eventually. \nUntil
    then, try not to lose what\u2019s left of your mind...\n\n\n8 - Finders Keepers,
    Losers Weepers: We aren\u2019t responsible for your stolen or lost belongings.
    \nIf your gold goes missing, cry me a river, then drown in it.\n\n9 - Embrace
    the Petty: Treat your fellow crew members like absolute garbage. \nIf you aren't
    being nasty and petty, you're doing it wrong."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
